FuncDef: This command configures a range of VC-ID values.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies a range of VC-ID values on an to be synchronized with a multi-chassis peer. Values-vc-id-range|start-vc-id-end-vc-id|, |start-vc-id|1 to 4294967295, |end-vc-id|1 to 4294967295.
Specifies a synchronization tag up to 32 characters in length to be used while synchronizing this encapsulation value range with the multi-chassis peer.
